{"tid":752731,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"是咁的，我想做低呢個樓市","createTime":"2018-07-23T04:54:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-23T16:01:12.000Z","uid":191019,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"46cd99aedc2d640ced55f2a67d8d3bca09a02492","tid":752731,"uid":191019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T04:54:37.000Z","msg":"一出世，香港就淪陷左<br />\n由細開始<br />\n加入邊度，邊度就會衰退<br />\n小學入樂團，小二有30個人，小五已經解散左，坐係鄰座的都一年內退學。<br />\n中學都係有鄰座問題，所以自己就選擇冇鄰座既位，但係偏要有女坐埋黎，唯有buff走佢，中學都有樂團，但一直都搞唔到好野。<br />\n一直以來，我去邊，邊度就有debuff<br />\n去多過3次的餐廳就會一個月內執7<br />\n(730執7的元朗燒雞排我都食左3次)<br />\n做全職甜品店甚至搞到老闆破產收場<br />\n於是我產生左一個念頭<br />\n去做地產<br />\n立志將香港的樓市壓到97年的時代"},{"pid":"0bf3ebda6467692c04fa57777c6fabaa8e1f14a4","tid":752731,"uid":45431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T04:55:45.000Z","msg":"你要做特首先有用喎"},{"pid":"0df131869ad09e209a91273c4ae05ebfc5f56def","tid":752731,"uid":134813,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T04:56:21.000Z","msg":"香港嘅未來 靠你喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef22f228b11048963bcea9fc2f693f74e50aaef7","tid":752731,"uid":171094,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T04:56:53.000Z","msg":"樓主不如入共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12f11da63d7dc89abcba58ca5eca0bc53bdc6a18","tid":752731,"uid":3764,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T04:56:55.000Z","msg":"睇到有d尷尬"},{"pid":"b5eb56c60c282daa29a3b12be163c7e92cccce55","tid":752731,"uid":85232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T04:57:10.000Z","msg":"樓主冇食過M記，大快活啲連鎖鋪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd616275736228cf3ad269992d7c05f9b33ff556","tid":752731,"uid":128805,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T04:57:31.000Z","msg":"共產黨需要你"},{"pid":"b88871b78ce56df094e828d5cd030d5fe74ba258","tid":752731,"uid":191019,"l